<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <link rel = "stylesheet"
          type = "text/css"
          href = "style.css" />
    <title>https://www.redhat.com/pt-br</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="upper-menu">
            <ul class="upper-left">
                <li><a href="#apps">Websites e apps</a></li>
            </ul>
            <ul class="upper-right">
                <li><a href="#idioma">Postuguês</a></li>
                <li><a href="#login">Login</a></li>
                <li><a href="#pesquisa">Pesquisa</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="main-menu">
            <div class="logo-div">
                <img src="logo-red-hat.svg" title="Red Hat">
            </div>
            <div class="navigation-bar">
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#produtos">Produtos</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#soluções">Soluções</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#serviços-e-suporte">Serviços e Suporte</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#recursos">Recursos</a></li>
                    <li><a href="red-hat-e-o-open-source">Red Hat e o open source</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="background-image">
                <img src="background.png" alt="imagem de fundo">
            </div>
            <div class="text">
                <h1 class="main-title centered-align"><span>Conecte tudo</span><span>com a cloud híbrida</span></h1>
                <p class="centered-align">A flexibilidade que você precisa para executar as cargas de trabalho no ambiente da sua escolha</p>
                <div class="centered-align">
                    <a href="#descubra">Descubra como</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="extra"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
            <div class="card">
                <img src="virtual-event-600x337.jpg" class="card-image">
                <div class="cardBody">
                        <h1 class="cardTitle">Join our hybrid cloud virtual event</h1>
                    <span>Discover how open architecture, processes, and culture can complete your cloud strategy.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="cardFooter">
                    <a class="cardButton" href=""><span style="margin: 10px">Watch on-demand</span></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="Card-Image-CLH-600x337-ICON.png" class="card-image">
                <div class="cardBody">
                    <h1 class="cardTitle">Command Line Heroes Season 3</h1>
                    <span>This season explores the epic stories of programming languages that shape technology.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="cardFooter">
                    <a class="cardButton" href="">Listen to the podcast</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
                <img src="fedora-table-600x337.jpg" class="card-image">
                <div class="cardBody">
                    <h1 class="cardTitle">Open culture</h1>
                    <span>Our open processes and culture help create open technologies to support enterprise IT.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="cardFooter">
                    <a class="cardButton" href="">See how we work</a>
                </div>
            </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
